title: 172: Separating Prospects; Quincy Wilson & Malachi Dupre interviews
itunes:title: 172: Separating Prospects; Quincy Wilson & Malachi Dupre interviews
description:
Former NFL Scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks review Notre Dame head coach Brian Kelly's controversial remarks on former Irish QB DeShone Kizer. The guys then try to separate and rank groupings of top prospects. Lastly, Florida cornerback Quincy Wilson and LSU wide receiver Malachi Dupre join the show.
